# To2048

To2048 game developed by Qt C++.

## resources

Please add your coustom images, the list:

- images of all grids

    mywidget.cpp -> MyWidget::loadFigures()

- window icon

    To2048.ui -> widget:QMainWindow -> property:windowIcon

- exe ico

    CMakeLists.txt -> add_executable(${PROJECT_NAME} ...)

    in this struct, add one line to locate your logo.rc

    e.g.

    add "./img/logo.rc"

    ```
    add_executable(${PROJECT_NAME}
        WIN32 # If you need a terminal for debug, please comment this statement 
        ${srcs} 
        "./img/logo.rc"
    ) 
    ```

    and the content of logo.rc file is:

    ```
    IDI_ICON1	ICON	DISCARDABLE	"logo.ico"
    ```

    the files logo.ico and logo.rc are in the same path, e.g. img/

- other img: img.jpg、voctory.png、defeat.png

    To2048.cpp -> To2048::To2048()


